We leveraged original model (LSTM Hidden Size/Output size: 4096/512) of the ELMo embeddings shared in https://allennlp.org/elmo portal.

Download the weight_file "elmo_2x4096_512_2048cnn_2xhighway_weights.hdf5" from the given link and put it inside ./embeddings/elmo directory.
Link: https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/allennlp/models/elmo/2x4096_512_2048cnn_2xhighway/elmo_2x4096_512_2048cnn_2xhighway_weights.hdf5
The required options_file is already provided in ./embeddings/elmo directory.